question: Who are the authors that published research papers about level demand in 'Int. J. Inf. Syst. Supply Chain Manag.' in the year '2018'?
query: SELECT DISTINCT ?answer WHERE { ?x dblp:title ?t . FILTER CONTAINS (LCASE(?t), "level demand") . ?x dblp:publishedIn 'Int. J. Inf. Syst. Supply Chain Manag.' . FILTER CONTAINS(LCASE('Int. J. Inf. Syst. Supply Chain Manag.'), 'Int. J. Inf. Syst. Supply Chain Manag.') . ?x dblp:year ?y . FILTER(?y = '2018') . ?x dblp:authoredBy ?answer }
